desc_short	-----								Johnny Graves—The Unchosen One is an action RPG set in an urban fantasy environment. It is a story-driven, hack and slash, single player game for PC. You play as Johnny, a magic revolver wielding man who has one night to close the gates of Hell, with Satan's monsters on his case.							
